        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/3ab097/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-06-28T00:04:54.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>A buddy has offered his allocation of cab and syrah at cost.   I note low scores the last few years from Vinuous, and a reference to a new winemaker.<br>\nI\u2019ve had older Arujao from the late '90\u2019s and earlier '00\u2019s but nothing recent. Any references or tastings of the '14, particularly the syrah?</p>",
